name: With My Hands Lifted Up
chorusText:
With my hands lifted up
And my mouth filled with praise
With a heart of thanksgiving
I will praise Thee, o Lord
I will praise Thee, o Lord
I will praise Thee, o Lord
With a heart of thanksgiving
I will praise Thee, o Lord
Met my hande omhoogMet elke klank wat ek singWil ek u kom verhoog en al my lof aan u bringWant U is my Skepper, U is my VriendDie heem’le lig U omhoogU word vir ewig vereerAan my Koning my Heer, ja my Jesus wat leefOns wil U net prys, Heer, ons wil U net prys
